# Webhook channel: generic HTTP relay; any client can POST /message and get a reply.
# Core connection: use channels/.env (core_host, core_port, CORE_API_KEY).
# Copy to .env and set values if you need to override defaults (host/port are also in config.yml).

# Optional: host/port this channel listens on (default 8005 / 0.0.0.0)
# WEBHOOK_HOST=0.0.0.0
# WEBHOOK_PORT=8005
